GOVERNMENT OF INDIA
CABINET SECRETARIAT
New Delhi, the 30th January,
****
The undersigned is directed to inform Members of the
Council of Ministers that Dr. Kailas Nath Katju, relinquished
the office of Cabinet Minister with effect from the afternoon
of the 30th January, 1957.
The Prime Minister will hold charge of the Ministry of
1957.
All Members of the Council of Ministers.
